snippet.title: Mario & Sonic at the London 2012 Olympic Games: Virtual Card Album (Nintendo 3DS Preview)
snippet.description:
Mario & Sonic at the London 2012 Olympic Games: Virtual Card Album is, as its name implies, a virtual card album where you can exchange them for Streetpass or receive them for Spotpass and finally buy them with game coins.

#Nintendo #N3DS #Cards
